# HLAE 2.124.2 (2021-11-28T09:04Z)
* Included AfxHookGoldSrc 1.104.0 (2021-11-28T09:04Z).
* Fixed the HLAE project to support Debug builds again, see how_to_build.txt for instructions.

## AfxHookSource 1.104.0 (2021-11-28T09:04Z)
* mirv_agr export: try to fix viewmodel / camera discrepancy in GOTV. Do not forget smoother demos guide, even when recording AGR only.
* Fixed afx_interop v7 getting stuck, by removing queued rendering indication and handling (now always indicates it to be non-queued, there were simply too many problems with detecting if we need to flush or not).
